{"tid":749491,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最恐怖犯規？歐聯外圍賽驚現「雙腳穿心腿」！","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T14:21:49.000Z","uid":31314,"like":118,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"150f809ef385ab3de0faf9a9c6ecfa6ccc9a9493","tid":749491,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"周二歐聯外圍賽資格賽上，匈牙利聯賽冠軍維迪奧頓（MOL Vidi FC）主場迎戰盧森堡冠軍F91迪德朗日（F91 Dudelange），首回合作客1:1逼和對手的維迪奧頓，周二回到主場戰至58分鐘已錄得2:1領先，只要將賽果守到完場就能晉級。然而急切追和的客軍，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>法國籍守將Bryan Melisse於下半場補時四分鐘，上演了堪稱「史上最糟糕犯規」的一幕，最終被球證紅牌趕離場。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n據了解，主角Bryan Melisse一直在低組別聯賽效力，事發時他起腳踢了皮球後，並沒有放下雙腳，反之突然向跑來追波的敵方球員Mate Patkai施以「雙腳穿心腿」，徹底地將帶有鞋釘的球鞋，踩在對手的肚子。後者被踩後隨即倒地面狀痛苦，球證亦立即當機立斷出示紅牌將Bryan Melisse趕離場，最終這名惡人效力的F91迪德朗日，亦以總比數2:3落敗無緣晉級。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/132301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F132301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=46316c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/132304_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F132304_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bb01eb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s7nPsC6p9Yc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs7nPsC6p9Yc&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w04zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6596ca43\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s7nPsC6p9Yc</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e47a2bd2d662069dec634afcdf9fa6acd9744e0","tid":749491,"uid":40940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20